data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Charming 3 bedroom and 2 bathroom 2-car-garage home nestled on a 7, 358 SqFt. corner lot in a quite and peaceful street located in the sought after community of Parkview Pointe. This cozy home features large open spaces with high ceilings and lots of natural light flowing through.  As you enter, you are greeted by a spacious living room and dining room with large windows next to a cozy bright kitchen with a breakfast nook. The closed-in porch provides an additional sitting area for your guests. Large bedrooms and bathrooms make this house perfect for a family. Some improvements include: New roof, water heater (3 years old), grab bars in toilet enclosure & roll in wheelchair accessible shower.This wonderful home is conveniently located near parks, schools, restaurants, shops and super markets.
